# Safety Notes

## Current Intent
This file is used to collect safety-related notes during early project planning.

## Key Hazards
- hydraulic pressure
- stored energy
- pinch points
- rotating spindle components
- moving cylinders
- glass breakage
- electrical control hazards

## Planned Safety Concepts
- emergency stop circuit
- high-pressure shutdown
- low-pressure shutdown
- motor stop circuit
- directional control interlocks
- pressure limiting using reducing valves
- guarded moving components
- controlled reset after faults

## Important Reminder
This repository is currently a planning and documentation space. Any future physical implementation will require formal review of:
- machine guarding
- hydraulic protection
- electrical protection
- lockout/tagout
- emergency stop function
- operator safety
- maintenance safety
